apacity is sufficiently large. Overall, our\nresults would help reveal practically achievable throughput performance of\nC-RAN, and lead to more efficient deployment of C-RAN in the next-generation\nwireless communication systems.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 15 Jul 2014 00:59:29 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 13 Nov 2014 06:23:14 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Sat, 15 Nov 2014 06:19:55 GMT"},{"version":"v4","created":"Tue, 14 Apr 2015 10:53:40 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-04-15"}
