agnetic nanoparticles in a vacuum in a non-uniform external magnetic\nfield is also considered taking into account the precession of the unit\nmagnetization vector and director.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 15 Jul 2014 12:47:55 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-01-08"}
